cc:Work.dc:title: Venus
cc:Work.dc:description: A bitmap trace of a true colour photograph of the planet Venus. Image is from the public domain file in Wikipedia - en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Venus-real.jpg. The Gimp was used to clean up, reduce colours, and scale the image. Inscape Simplify and a Blur of one was used to reduce the svg size and give it more realism.
